<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="97" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[118,768,1011,1264]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">
The type of 
<taxonomicName box="[285,620,1011,1035]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="marginatum" variety="intermedium">
<emphasis box="[285,439,1011,1035]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">B. marginatum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[489,620,1011,1035]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">intermedium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was indicated by Hassler in the original description as 
<emphasis box="[536,722,1044,1068]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">Hassler 8237 p.p.</emphasis>
(i.e. 
<emphasis box="[118,219,1077,1101]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">pro parte</emphasis>
). To make the distinction with the 
<typeStatus box="[601,648,1077,1101]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">type</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" form="fruticosum" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="form" species="marginatum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">B. marginatum</emphasis>
f. 
<emphasis box="[231,343,1109,1133]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">fruticosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on part of the same gathering (see above) the letter [a] has been added to this particular specimen. Hassler did annotate it with his own handwriting: 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">
“ 
<taxonomicName authority="Hassler" authorityName="Hassler" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="marginatum" subSpecies="meridionale" variety="intermedium">Bombax marginatum K. Sch. subspec. meridionale Hassler var.</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
<emphasis box="[118,357,1240,1264]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">intermedium Hassler”</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
